About.Hours & facilities:
A volunteer member from the group is available each Tuesday 10am-12 noon and Wednesday 2-4pm to assist with family history research.
Additional information should be adressed to the Secretary, YPFHG, PO Box 260, Kadina SA 5554. Fees apply. An ssae is to be enclosed for reply. Information brochure outlining fees available on request.

About.Access: Minimum age 15 years. 1 week's advance notice of visit required.

About.Acquisition focus: Local and family history pertaining to area.

Contact.Street address: Local History Room, Kadina Community Library, TAFE Complex, 1A Doswell Tce, Kadina SA 5554
